Package: ouija
Type: Package
Title: Incorporating prior knowledge in single-cell trajectory learning
        using Bayesian nonlinear factor analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2017-07-29
Authors@R: person("Kieran", "Campbell", email = "kieranrcampbell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Ouija learns trajectories or 'pseudotimes' from single-cell RNA-seq data. Using Bayesian 
  nonlinear factor analysis biological knowledge of gene expression across pseudotime can be
  encoded as informative priors in the model.
License: GPL (>=3)
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), Rcpp (>= 0.12.0)
Imports: rstan (>= 2.9.0), ggplot2, reshape2,
        dplyr, methods, stats, MCMCglmm, coda
Suggests: viridis, cowplot, tidyr
biocViews: Software, Transcriptomics, GeneExpression, RNASeq,
        SingleCell, Bayesian
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: rmarkdown, testthat, Biobase, scater, knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Author: Kieran Campbell [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kieran Campbell <kieranrcampbell@gmail.com>
